<zk>
    <label multiline="true">
        1. Fetch https://www.zkoss.org/2005/zul/zul.xsd
        2. Run a script that flattens every &lt;xs:attributeGroup ref="..." /&gt;
            and counts attribute names per attributeGroup / complexType
            (see find-duplicates.js in ZK-6060).
        3. Before the fix it reported duplicates such as:
            inputElementAttrGroup        : onOK, onCancel
            formatInputElementAttrGroup  : onOK, onCancel
            numberInputElementAttrGroup  : onOK, onCancel
            dateTimeInputElementAttrGroup: onOK, onCancel
            plus duplicates inside colorboxType (width/height),
            cropperType (onCancel), goldenpanelType (draggable/droppable),
            listboxType / windowType (onOK/onCancel) and timeboxType /
            timepickerType (constraint).
    </label>
</zk>